welcome_message_body: Welcome to Wolfratshausen, a charming town nestled in the beautiful Bavarian countryside! Known for its picturesque landscapes, rich history, and friendly locals, we invite you to immerse yourself in the unique culture and experience all that our city has to offer. Enjoy your stay and make unforgettable memories!
